'''Nikaweratiya Divisional Secretariat''' is a  [[Divisional Secretariats of Sri Lanka|Divisional Secretariat]]  of [[Kurunegala District]], of [[North Western Province, Sri Lanka|North Western Province]], [[Sri Lanka]]. 

